ds/2023/11/wide-awake-crowd-garry-jones-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wide-awake-crowd-garry-jones-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wide-awake-crowd-garry-jones-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/wide-awake-crowd-garry-jones-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3534967" class="wp-caption-text"> 2023 年“Wide Awake”上的人群。图片来源：Garry Jones/Press</figcaption></figure><p>与此同时，去年的活动由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/caroline-polachek">Caroline Polachek</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/caroline-polachek-to-headline-wide-awake-2023-festival-in-london-new-lineup-buy-tickets-3346583">领衔</a>，还邀请了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-segall">Ty Segall</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thee-oh-sees">Osees</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/a-place-to-bury-strangers">A Place To Bury Strangers</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/erol-alkan">Erol Alkan</a>等人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alex-g">Alex G</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/viagra-boys">Viagra Boys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-country-new-road">Black Country、New Road</a> 、Two Shell、Tirzah、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/los-bitchos">Los Bitchos</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/civic">Civic</a> 、Wasted Youth、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/clamm">Clamm</a> 、O.、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/artists/nice-biscuit">Nice Biscuit</a> 、JJUUJJUU 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warmduscher">Warmduscher</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-avery">Daniel Avery</a> （现场）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shygirl">Shygirl</a> 、 Coucou Chloe、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blondshell">Blondshell</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joy-orbison">Joy Orbison</a