://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-Zac-Efron@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-Zac-Efron@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Matthew-Perry-Zac-Efron@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>扎克·埃夫隆回应了已故<em>《老友记》</em>明星马修·佩里希望他在传记片中扮演他的报道。</p><p>上周（11 月 2 日）有消息<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/matthew-perry-was-planning-to-ask-zac-efron-play-him-in-biopic-3529334">称，这位演员将扎克·埃夫隆选为他在传记片中扮演自己的首选</a>，当时他的一位密友雅典娜·克罗斯比 (Athenna Crosby) 接受<a href="https://www.etonline.com/matthew-perry-wanted-this-co-star-to-play-him-in-the-biopic-he-was-working-on-friend-reveals-214044" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《今夜娱乐》</em></a>采访。</p><p>这次采访是在<em>《老友记》</em>演员于 10 月 28 日被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perry-dead-54-friends-tributes-3524335">发现死在洛杉矶的家中</a>之后进行的。他享年 54 岁，死亡与明显的溺水有关。</p><p> “他说他想拍一部关于他生活的电影，”克罗斯比说。 “他过去曾与扎克·埃夫隆合作过一部电影，他说他希望扎克·埃夫隆扮演他年轻版本的[他自己]，并且他很快就会要求他这样做。”</p><p>佩里和埃夫隆此前曾在 2009 年主演喜剧电影<em>《17 Again》</em> ，他们在片中分别扮演同一角色的年老版本和年轻版本。谈到这个角色，克罗斯比还回忆起佩里说埃夫隆当时扮演他“做得非常好”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="17 再次预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Dk9XtJI0Sao?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>现在，埃夫隆在新片<em>《铁爪》</em>的红地毯上发表讲话时解释说，他“很荣幸”听到佩里的赞扬。</p><p> “我很荣幸听到他想让我扮演他，”他周三（11 月 8 日）告诉<a href="https://www.hindustantimes.com/entertainment/hollywood/zac-efron-says-he-would-be-honoured-to-play-matthew-perry-in-future-biopic-i-looked-up-to-him-101699513018297.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志</em></a>。</p><p>他继续表示，这位演员去世的消息让他感到“震惊”，并补充道：“他是我的导师，我们一起制作了一部非常酷的电影。我尊敬他，我从他那里学到了喜剧的时机。 </p><figure id="attachment_3534899" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3534899" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3534899" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/17-again-premiere@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Actors Michelle Trachtenberg, Zac Efron, Leslie Mann and Matthew Perry arrive at the premiere of Warner Bros. &quot;17 Again&quot; held at Grauman's Chinese Theatre on April 14, 2009" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/17-again-premiere@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/17-again-premiere@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/17-again-premiere@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/17-again-premiere@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/17-again-premiere@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/17-again-premiere@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3534899" class="wp-caption-text"> Actors Michelle Trachtenberg, Zac Efron, Leslie Mann and Matthew Perry arrive at the premiere of Warner Bros. “17 Again” held at Grauman&#39;s Chinese Theatre on April 14, 2009. CREDIT: Kevin Winter/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> “I mean, when we were filming <em>17 Again</em> , it was so surreal for me to look across and have him be there, because I&#39;ve learned so much from him, from his whole life.”</p><p> Following news of his death, <em>Friends</em> co-creator <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/friends-co-creator-remembers-final-conversation-with-matthew-perry-3528046">Marta Kauffman also recalled her last conversation with Perry</a> , which took place two weeks before his death.</p><p> Describing him as being “happy and chipper”, she said: “He didn&#39;t seem weighed down by anything… He was in a really good place, which is why this seems so unfair.”</p><p> Perry&#39;s Friends co-stars <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/friends-stars-attend-funeral-of-matthew-perry-3530457">attended his Los Angeles funeral</a> last week, and it was also revealed that the actor could receive a <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/matthew-perry-could-receive-posthumous-star-on-hollywood-walk-of-fame-3531178">posthumous star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame</a> ..</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/zac-efron-responds-to-matthew-perry-wish-that-he-play-him-in-a-biopic-3534890">Zac Efron responds to Matthew Perry&#39;s wish that he play him in a biopic</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
